Simple .vim folder with vimrc and gvimrc config files for easy use on multiple machines

To clone repository:
	
	git clone https://github.com/AlexLutz/dotvim.git ~/.vim

To create symbolic links:

	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ls -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

To initialize and update submodules:

	git submodule init
	git submodule update

To upgrade all bundled plugins:

	git submodule foreach git pull origin master
